{{Otheruses|Kooroo}}
The '''Kooroo''' were a race of beings thought to have been the founders of the [[Fellowship of Kooroo]].

The species was never discovered by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], and the location and name of their homeworld remained unknown to outsiders. [[Shrine of Kooroo|Shrines]] possibly built by the Kooroo were found on many worlds in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]], including [[Boztrok]], [[Gelgelar/Legends|Gelgelar]], [[Sufezz]], and [[Branteez]].

